WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:10.277 --> 00:00:12.138
Should I get bangs?

00:00:12.138 --> 00:00:13.668
Why do you want to get bangs?

00:00:13.668 --> 00:00:16.578
I think it might help your look.

00:00:16.578 --> 00:00:18.948
That depends on the look you want.

00:00:18.948 --> 00:00:22.478
Bangs can make you look younger, or they’ll
make you look like a little girl.

00:00:22.478 --> 00:00:25.247
I thought it would look cool.

00:00:25.247 --> 00:00:29.428
Bangs do a bang up job of hiding acne on your
forehead, though the oil from your hair might

00:00:29.428 --> 00:00:30.588
make it worse.

00:00:30.588 --> 00:00:32.188
I don’t have acne.

00:00:32.188 --> 00:00:36.657
I do have trouble with maintaining a low maintenance
hairstyle.

00:00:36.657 --> 00:00:41.918
If you don’t have bangs, you can let your
hair grow out a few inches, as long as it

00:00:41.918 --> 00:00:42.918
isn’t colored.

00:00:42.918 --> 00:00:46.768
If you have bangs, you have to keep them trimmed
or you’ll look stupid with your hair in

00:00:46.768 --> 00:00:47.768
your eyes.

00:00:47.768 --> 00:00:50.128
Bangs are popular now.

00:00:50.128 --> 00:00:54.337
You can either pay someone $8 to trim them
or cut them yourself.

00:00:54.337 --> 00:00:55.538
Is that low maintenance?

00:00:55.538 --> 00:00:59.478
Bang trims do not cost that much.

00:00:59.478 --> 00:01:01.317
Depends on where you go.

00:01:01.317 --> 00:01:06.248
Some places may charge $5 for it, while others
may charge the full haircut price for a bang

00:01:06.248 --> 00:01:07.248
trim.

00:01:07.248 --> 00:01:09.558
Who shouldn’t get bangs?

00:01:09.558 --> 00:01:11.568
You shouldn’t get bangs if your hair is
ultra-curly.

00:01:11.568 --> 00:01:16.117
For most people, the curls in front look tacky.

00:01:16.117 --> 00:01:17.678
That isn’t me.

00:01:17.678 --> 00:01:20.728
How could I tell if bangs would look good
on me?

00:01:20.728 --> 00:01:23.608
You could put your hair in a pony tail and
hang that over the front of your face.

00:01:23.608 --> 00:01:26.859
If it looks bad, you know not to get bangs.

00:01:26.859 --> 00:01:31.368
Bangs don’t have to all be long.

00:01:31.368 --> 00:01:32.368
True.

00:01:32.368 --> 00:01:37.388
Long bangs look best on little kids and girls,
but they give women a youthful look.

00:01:37.388 --> 00:01:42.117
Short bangs are best for adults, but too short
looks silly, kind of like a girls’ comb-over.

00:01:42.117 --> 00:01:48.428
My hair isn’t long enough to make a ponytail,
much less drape if over my forehead.

00:01:48.428 --> 00:01:53.117
There are hair style software programs that
let you upload your picture and then try out

00:01:53.117 --> 00:01:54.357
different hairstyles.

00:01:54.357 --> 00:01:57.558
How much does that cost?

00:01:57.558 --> 00:02:01.978
Nothing, since the sites are paid by ads by
hairstylists.

00:02:01.978 --> 00:02:04.737
Or you could just see a hairstylist and ask
her in person.

